  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is being to see if participating in breathing exercise training and practicing&#xD;
      this training will help with Postural tachycardia syndrome (POTS). The information may help&#xD;
      doctors to learn more about how the different parts of people's brains communicate.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
